Paper: hep-th/0012235

Date: 2000-12-25

Title: On gravitational interaction of spin 3/2 Nambu-Goldstone fermion

Authors: Kazunari Shima and Motomu Tsuda

Comments: 6 pages, Latex, a comment added, some typos corrected, accepted for

publication in Physics Letters BJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B521 (2001) 67-70

A new gravitational interaction of spin 3/2 Nambu-Goldstone(N-G) fermion isconstructed, which gives a new framework for the consistent gravitationalcoupling of spin 3/2 massless field. The action is invariant under a new globalsupersymmetry.